N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 49.11 - Premises open to general public

State Regulations

Premises for which a bottle club license has been issued
shall be open to the general public. The term bottle clubs is not restricted to
clubs as defined under section
3
(9)
of the Alcoholic Beverage Control
